Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Commercial Services
Sub-Industry: Professional Services
Law Debenture Trust Company of New York operates as an international law firm. The Company provides legal services in a wide range of areas including corporate and pension trusts, agent for service of process, treasury management, mergers and acquisitions for SPVs, and structured finance administration. Law Debenture Trust serves clients worldwide.




