Company Overview of Law Debenture Trust Company of New York



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Law Debenture Trust Company of New York provides indenture trustee, paying agent, and registrar services. It offers escrow, project finance, agency, administrative, and other non-traditional fiduciary services, as well as successor trustee services for default and bankruptcy, and liquidation situations. Law Debenture’s escrow solutions include M and A transactions; litigation or claims settlement trusts and escrows; reinsurance trusts; payment and/or securities allocation escrows; 1031 exchange or ‘Like-Kind Escrows’; and bankruptcy liquidation, document custodian, cash deposit, contractor lien retention, landfill closure escrows/environmental, and subscription escrows. The company also offe...
Law Debenture Trust Company of New York provides indenture trustee, paying agent, and registrar services. It offers escrow, project finance, agency, administrative, and other non-traditional fiduciary services, as well as successor trustee services for default and bankruptcy, and liquidation situations. Law Debenture’s escrow solutions include M and A transactions; litigation or claims settlement trusts and escrows; reinsurance trusts; payment and/or securities allocation escrows; 1031 exchange or ‘Like-Kind Escrows’; and bankruptcy liquidation, document custodian, cash deposit, contractor lien retention, landfill closure escrows/environmental, and subscription escrows. The company also offers corporate trust services for corporations, sovereigns, and municipalities, which raises capital by issuing debt obligations. In addition, it offers administrative agent services, such as monitoring loan covenants, facilitating assignments/transfers, performing waterfall calculations, executing investment instructions, reviewing amendments, and providing account reporting; receipt and account for cash; and disbursing funds to cover project costs or for debt service. Further, the company provides collateral agent services. It serves companies, law firms, and individuals in the United States and internationally. The company was founded in 2002 and is based in New York, New York with offices in London, New York, and Hong Kong. As of December 6, 2016, Law Debenture Trust Company of New York operates as a subsidiary of Delaware Trust Company.
